      "settings": {
        "desc_eyebrow": "Your Drive",
        "desc_heading": "What to expect.",
        "desc_heading_accent": "Minute by minute.",
        "description": "<p>Twenty kilometres south of Dubai, the sand changes colour — from pale beige to deep ochre to Al Badayer's signature rust red. This is where we put you behind the wheel.</p><p>Your Polaris RZR 1000cc is the same machine the pros race in the Abu Dhabi Desert Challenge. Four-wheel drive, full cage, five-point harness, power steering. After a fifteen-minute briefing with your marshal you'll be leading a convoy across open desert, chasing the horizon through dune bowls up to thirty feet high.</p><p>Unlike the quad-bike tours that run in circles behind a fence, our route is a proper point-to-point. You'll cover fifteen to forty kilometres of untouched sand, stop for Arabic coffee on a ridge, and return as the call to prayer drifts across the dunes.</p>",
        "tl_eyebrow": "Your Evening",
        "tl_heading": "Six moments.",
        "tl_heading_accent": "Two unforgettable hours.",
        "tl_lede": "From the moment we collect you at your hotel to the tea on the ridge — here's how every Dune Buggy booking unfolds."
      }
    },
    "faq": {
      "type": "dlh-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_1": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do I need a driving licence?",
            "answer": "Yes — you'll need to present a valid licence (international or home country). Passengers over 16 can ride without one. Under-16s must be accompanied in the two- or four-seater variants."
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What's the cancellation policy?",
            "answer": "Free cancellation up to 24 hours before your start time — full refund, no questions. Cancellations within 24 hours are non-refundable but can be rescheduled once."
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it safe for first-timers?",
            "answer": "Absolutely. 70% of our drivers have never touched a buggy before. Our marshals run a 15-min briefing, convoy the whole route, and match pace to the slowest driver. Zero pressure to floor it."
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What should I wear?",
            "answer": "Closed shoes (no flip-flops), comfortable trousers, sunglasses. We provide the helmet, gloves, goggles and a scarf. Avoid loose scarves or jewellery."
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Where do we meet?",
            "answer": "Hotel pickup is available for free within Dubai city limits. Otherwise meet at our Al Badayer staging point — live pin shared 24h before your slot."
          }
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it suitable for children?",
            "answer": "Kids 6+ can ride as passengers in the two- or four-seater. Minimum driving age is 18 with a valid licence. We offer a family-friendly route with gentler dunes."
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": ["faq_1", "faq_2", "faq_3", "faq_4", "faq_5", "faq_6"],
